section.para:
Creating and building a simple example. We will create a simple
            Qt Embedded application and use qmake2 and
            make to cross compile.


$ . /usr/local/angstrom/arm/environment-setup
$ cd $HOME
$ mkdir qte-example
$ cd qte-example

$ echo "TEMPLATE=app
SOURCES=main.cpp
" > qte-example.pro

$ echo '#include <QApplication>
#include <QPushButton>

int main(int argc, char** argv) {
    QApplication app(argc, argv);

    QPushButton btn("Hello World");
    btn.show();
    btn.showMaximized();

    return app.exec();
}
' > main.cpp

$ qmake2
$ make
